text: Les hautes solitudes is a 1974 French experimental film written, directed and produced by Philippe Garrel. It stars Jean Seberg with Nico, Tina Aumont and Laurent Terzieff. Originally released in France in 1974, it was screened in New York's Metrograph in 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1974 films Category:French films Category:Films directed by Philippe Garrel
